</p></note></section><section id="GUID-EC9C24D5-D455-4022-B616-D7FEF4DE0A1A" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Illustration</title><fig id="GUID-1C6A5506-8461-4BFD-8B7C-FB47C7EF289A" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-ED64BFF0-4BD9-4E0C-86C7-424BB2D0A44A-low.png" id="IMAGE_246C5CF278EB49F9A18725FDE7AC3792" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-ED64BFF0-4BD9-4E0C-86C7-424BB2D0A44A-low.png"/></fig></section><section id="SECTION_3C9A6B084A3F4FB0B62AF616DEDC3247" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">How to remove</title><table pgwide="1" id="TABLE_99C7ABA5064244CA8F6FC70BC350CF9A" class="- topic/table "><tgroup align="left" outputclass="step" cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead valign="top" class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remarks 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody valign="top" class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Remove the black bracket from the axis. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Use the small screwdriver to push the black plastic part of the axis on both sides away from the unit. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Only push at the top of the plastic part otherwise you will break the axis holder. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="FIG_A55A446E77AE469DBD32ACB32746E2E9" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-41604E46-78CE-4BE1-B9EB-C23A8115670A-low.png" id="IMAGE_86E9BF5B6B1B4648A46EFA4D69AA2DA8" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-41604E46-78CE-4BE1-B9EB-C23A8115670A-low.png"/></fig><fig id="FIG_24F58C5EB9334B75B1E48FD43BBE9C65" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-E0E123F8-0999-4CAC-889D-0E9B6CC862C8-low.png" id="IMAGE_9D4FC30A2DE74381BAE611489F27F294" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-E0E123F8-0999-4CAC-889D-0E9B6CC862C8-low.png"/></fig><fig id="FIG_2AD054FE87534877A5F9C9388794D8D6" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-657F8E2B-C983-4B10-B138-7F2417AEF99B-low.png" id="IMAGE_D27F9A038DC04E1C834343077AD37BAE" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-657F8E2B-C983-4B10-B138-7F2417AEF99B-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-6E802311-FAEC-4496-9722-5131B0CE729D" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-48A16463-F289-47E6-BB22-0A67C3129F68-low.png" id="IMAGE_425342D6A12F47F6999D4C9193B479D1" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-48A16463-F289-47E6-BB22-0A67C3129F68-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the axis of the roller. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="FIG_E772B0664A8B4EC6896D3D40130AD800" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-27F74C8F-8712-4100-B016-DBFE176F5AB4-low.png" id="IMAGE_0555353D6ACA4A9BB1CEC1FF1E598F32" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-27F74C8F-8712-4100-B016-DBFE176F5AB4-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the roller. 
